            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/23/35428890/56a7afb2342c71f6d852a1470599e4e6_7132532244330983865.png",
                "id": "talent39518",
                "key": "Parthian Shot",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Parthian Shot"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>. This character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Manifest Gale</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Manifest Gale</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached uses Charged Attack:</span> Spend 1 less <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Unaligned Element</span>, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>, and attaches <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pressurized Collapse</span> to the target character.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Pressurized Collapse</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase: </span>Switch the character to which this is attached to be the Active Character.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span><br>(Only 1 such effect can be on the same side of the playing field)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/23/35428890/6f3f1e66aac8d91ecca768d4a7f48e56_7320953545979900787.png",
                "id": "talent94725",
                "key": "Wind Realm of Nasamjnin ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Wind Realm of Nasamjnin "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span><br>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>, summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dazzling Polyhedron</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/23/35428890/bec3c6e3c0067cc3e0340d50df63f27e_5855515682494097274.png",
                "id": "talent97559",
                "key": "The Wind's Secret Ways",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "The Wind's Secret Ways"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 3</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When this Summon is on the field:</span> Opposing character(s) take +1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/23/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4032079438475335747.png",
                "id": "talent21887",
                "key": "Dazzling Polyhedron",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/23/35428890/7c29f5ce38f0d332fbd3113f1b605a5c_6013261285954663422.png",
                "title": "Dazzling Polyhedron"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Reacts with Elements if they are already applied:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Cryo DMG to all opposing chracters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Swirl:</span> Deals 1 Hydro DMG to all opposing characters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Pyro DMG to all opposing characters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Electro DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/23/35428890/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_2321094926902032368.png",
                "id": "talent30186",
                "key": "Anemo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Anemo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Charged Attack</span></strong><br>Before your Action Phase, should the total number of your Elemental Dice be even, your Normal Attack will be considered a Charged Attack.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Unaligned Element</span></strong><br>You may use Elemental Dice of any element to pay this type of cost.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/23/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_1410971794065557697.png",
